OL,3,CMan jailed for the 'violent murder' of
OL,4,Chis mum
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for life for the
OL,7,F'violent murder' of his mum after
OL,8,Ftread patterns from his trainers was
OL,9,Fmatched to marks on her body.
OL,11,FStephen Ball, 32, of Pear Avenue, Bury
OL,12,Fwas sentenced to life imprisonment
OL,13,Fwith a minimum of 15 years for the
OL,14,Fvicious murder of his mum, Suzanne
OL,15,FGalvin.
