OL,3,CMan jailed for the 'violent murder' of
OL,4,Chis mum
OL,6,FOn Friday 1 November, Bolton Crown
OL,7,FCourt heard how a disturbance was
OL,8,Freported at the address of the Ball's
OL,9,Fmum with a man shouting for his mum to
OL,10,Flet him in just before 8pm on 16th
OL,11,FSeptember 2023.
OL,13,FShortly after this time, Ball made a
OL,14,Fcall to his grandmother, who lives in
OL,15,FIreland, telling her that he had come
OL,16,Fback to the flat to find his mother
OL,17,Finjured and she was struggling to
OL,18,Fbreathe. He told her that his mum's
OL,19,Fwrist was broken, and she had bruising
OL,20,Fto her eyes and shoulder.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
