OL,3,CMan jailed for the 'violent murder' of
OL,4,Chis mum
OL,6,FAs police attended the reported
OL,7,Fdisturbance, Suzanne was found
OL,8,Funresponsive on a mattress on the
OL,9,Ffloor, with visible blood and
OL,10,Fextensive bruising. Ball was also in
OL,11,Fthe flat and when asked, he provided
OL,12,Fconflicting accounts of how his
OL,13,Fmother's extensive injuries all over
OL,14,Fher body had occurred.
OL,16,FSadly, Suzanne passed away from her
OL,17,Finjuries on Monday 18 September 2023,
OL,18,Fwith Ball subsequently being charged
OL,19,Fwith her murder two days later.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
