OL,3,CMan jailed for the 'violent murder' of
OL,4,Chis mum
OL,6,FWhen initially arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof assault on the 16th September 2023,
OL,8,Fa pair of Ball's trainers had been
OL,9,Fseized - the tread pattern of which
OL,10,Fproved to be a match for some of the
OL,11,Fmarks on his mum's skin.
OL,13,FSenior Investigating Officer, Duncan
OL,14,FThorpe said: "Firstly, our thoughts
OL,15,Fand prayers remain with Mary,
OL,16,FSuzanne's mum and Stephen's
OL,17,Fgrandmother, who has lost her daughter
OL,18,Fin the most terrible of circumstances.
