OL,3,CMan jailed for the 'violent murder' of
OL,4,Chis mum
OL,6,F"This was a drug induced violent and
OL,7,Fsustained assault on a lady who was
OL,8,Fcompletely innocent. Whatever sentence
OL,9,Fwas imposed today, sadly it will not
OL,10,Fbring Suzanne back."
OL,12,F"Violence against women and girls
OL,13,Fremains a priority for GMP and we will
OL,14,Fdo everything in our power to ensure
OL,15,Fthose who commit these offences are
OL,16,Fidentified, charged and brought to
OL,17,Fjustice.
